WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.152 --> 00:00:12.433
We start in the demonstration, with the installation of two type 1 rails, at a distance of 440 mm from each other.

2
00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:21.581
Thus, a type 440 module can be placed between the two rails

3
00:00:21.681 --> 00:00:26.482
Further modules of type 440 can thus also be arranged as desired

4
00:00:26.582 --> 00:00:34.245
Combination with Type 1 modules is also possible

5
00:00:34.345 --> 00:00:40.872
Use the flexibility and set up your workspace according to your requirements and wishes

6
00:00:40.972 --> 00:00:50.620
If sufficient wall space is available, we recommend using rails of Type 110 to also make optimal use of the respective outer area.

7
00:00:50.721 --> 00:01:00.709
For example, by placing a knife sharpener, a magnetic board for your notes, a paper roll holder

8
00:01:00.809 --> 00:01:06.204
or a glove dispenser that extends vertically

9
00:01:06.304 --> 00:01:09.253
or can also be attached horizontally

10
00:01:09.353 --> 00:01:19.304
You can expand your system at any time and equip it with further modules and thus position everything clearly and within easy reach.

11
00:01:19.404 --> 00:01:33.690
In this way, two Type 440 modules can be exchanged for a Type 990 module in no time.

12
00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:47.659
Depending on the space available, your modular system can be freely scaled to suit the flexible use of other modules.

13
00:01:47.759 --> 00:02:02.283
A short rail allows you, in addition to attaching a wall shelf, to attach various modules of type 1 or 110.

14
00:02:02.383 --> 00:02:09.025
Wall shelves can also be optionally expanded on the underside by attaching a hook bar to make optimal use of the space underneath.

15
00:02:09.125 --> 00:02:17.138
Individual rails also enable a space-saving, clear arrangement of your utensils.

16
00:02:17.238 --> 00:02:26.229
Don't waste your time searching in drawers. Position your modules and utensils, visible, ergonomic and handy.

17
00:02:26.329 --> 00:02:31.329
Benefit from our ever-growing range, optimise your processes and thus save valuable time. The modular system of chef modules gives you the freedom to change.
